---
title: Roasted Cauliflower and Farro Bowls with Smoky Hummus Drizzle
description: Texture, texture, texture! Chewy sweet sultanas, tender lentils, creamy feta, roasty cauliflower and hearty farro make a satisfying veggie set! Lemony, smoky hummus sauce is delicious drizzled over every bite.
